io.github.retrooper.packetevents.event.annotation

Annotation Type PacketHandler

  • Deprecated. 
    Was used for the old event system, the new one doesn't need this anymore.

    @Target(value=METHOD)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Deprecated
public @interface PacketHandler
    This is what you override your event listener with on the old event system. You can specify the event priority of the listener method.
